ps.ledscroller%26fbclid%3DIwAR2XjBA9Ve-uOi9HiYVqsbv1ZVZe8NaYiRNUYNoGtaFF1fAjUPXWY4se1L0&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9xxV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=c60bc233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=oops.ledscroller&amp;fbclid=IwAR2XjBA9Ve-uOi9HiYVqsbv1ZVZe8NaYiRNUYNoGtaFF1fAjUPXWY4se1L0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有tablet仲正! 會好搶眼!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好靜坐範圍外痴Memo，機管局轉曬超高清cam，班人真係會成日望住cam。之前有人話塞機埸，班AA淆到第二日就轉cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到全世界都知香港警黑勾結!!打999比人cut線!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n***呢個template可以攞去幫推呀***<br />\n***醫護界都好似需要幫手推 Popo唔理住啦***<br />\n***若有唔認同嘅post留下正負皮 再推有用post***<br />\n<br />\n持續更新 以上為09:00更新版本"},{"pid":"15df72f57593e1e2750bcb462f55158ce23b3f45","tid":1366623,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"連仔可唔可以置頂？"},{"pid":"2a05bbc486f2eaccdf28dfd215601d069fa8cc8a","tid":1366623,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"謝樓主本合。有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8a92f113bcadc90a1f786342d05a9ff63c9f06","tid":1366623,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"[突發有圖] [7